─────────────────────────
Every error should be logged with:

{
  "timestamp": "2026-03-28T10:30:00Z",
  "error_type": "payment_failed",
  "context": "Customer checkout",
  "details": "Card declined",
  "user_id": "12345",
  "attempted_fix": true,
