DATA PROCESSING
• Parse JSON/CSV
• Run calculations
• Generate reports
• Create charts
• Export data

5.5 SECURITY BEST PRACTICES
────────────────────────────
• Never expose API keys in code
• Use environment variables
• Rotate keys regularly
• Limit permissions (least privilege)
• Log all API calls
• Verify webhooks signatures
• Sanitize user input
• Encrypt sensitive data at rest

