───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
MODULE 6: MONETIZATION STRATEGIES
───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

6.1 PRICING MODELS
───────────────────
Choose your model:

SUBSCRIPTION (SaaS)
• Monthly/annual fee
• Predictable revenue
• Requires ongoing value
• Examples: $29/mo, $249/yr

PER-USAGE
• Pay per action
• Scales with value
• Good for variable needs
• Examples: $0.10/email, $1/task

FREEMIUM
• Free basic tier
• Paid upgrades
• Low barrier to entry
• Examples: 100 free, then $10/mo

ONE-TIME PAYMENT
• Lifetime license
• Simple for customers
• Need new products for revenue
• Examples: $199 once

6.2 PRICING PSYCHOLOGY
────────────────────────
Key principles:

ANCHORING
Show high option first, making mid look reasonable.
$97 (Pro) vs $297 (Business) vs $97 (Starter)

ODD NUMBERS
Use $47 instead of $50.
Creates perception of deal.

CONTRAST
Show what they get vs. what they pay.
"10 hours saved/week for less than $1/day"

DECISION SIMPLICITY
Max 3 pricing tiers.
Too many options = paralysis.

GEOGRAPHIC PRICING
Lower prices for developing markets.
Increases accessibility, builds goodwill.

6.3 DIGITAL PRODUCTS
────────────────────
High-margin products to create:

TEMPLATES & PROMPTS
• Low production cost
• Instant delivery
• High perceived value
• Examples: $5-50

EBOOKS & GUIDES
• One-time creation
• Evergreen content
• Passive income
• Examples: $19-97

VIDEO COURSES
• Higher production
• Premium pricing
• Community potential
• Examples: $97-497

SOFTWARE/TOOLS
• Highest effort
• Highest recurring revenue
• Competitive moat
• Examples: $29-299/mo

6.4 REVENUE STREAMS
────────────────────
Diversify across:

DIRECT SALES
• Your website
• Higher margin
• Full control
• Requires traffic

MARKETPLACES
• Gumroad, Payhip, etc.
• Built-in audience
• Lower margin
• Easier to start

AFFILIATE
• Promote others' products
• Earn commissions
• No product creation
• $100-1000s/mo possible

SERVICES
• Consulting, setup
• Premium hourly rate
• Human touch
• Scales with time

6.5 SALES FUNNELS
──────────────────
Build automated funnels:

LEAD MAGNET
Free value → Email capture
"Get my free AI prompt pack"

BRIDGE
Email sequence → Build trust
"Here's how to use AI for business"

TRAP
Low-ticket offer → Demonstrate value
"$5 prompt pack, instant delivery"

CORE
Main product → Resolution
"$97 masterclass, comprehensive training"

EXIT
Upsell → Higher value
"Get 1-on-1 coaching for $497"

6.6 SCALING TO $10K/MONTH
───────────────────────────
Path from $0 to $10K:

$0-$1K (Month 1-2):
• Launch first product
• Get first 10 customers
• Build case studies
• Start email list

$1K-$3K (Month 3-4):
• Launch second product
• Increase prices
• Add affiliate program
• Build community

$3K-$5K (Month 5-6):
• Launch course
• Add subscription tier
• Automate marketing
• Hire VA for support

$5K-$10K (Month 7-12):
• Multiple products
• Enterprise clients
• Partnerships
• Team expansion

KEY METRICS TO HIT:
• $100/customer average
• 100 paying customers
• 30% margins
• 10% monthly growth

