• Over-deliver on support

HANDLING ISSUES:
• Bugs → Fix fast, compensate
• Feature gaps → Roadmap, workaround
• Expectations → Realign, refund if needed
• Complaints → Address publicly, fix privately

BUILDING LOYALTY:
• Thank them personally
• Give early access to features
• Credit them in updates
• Involve in decisions

